<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Lieber Hans, als ir uns <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> Spieszin <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burg<ex>er</ex>in</expan>
<add><expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan></add>, <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                        sie durch <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>wille<ex>n</ex></expan> besant und mit ir geredt also, daz sie
                            <expan>hieczwisch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> und <app><note><q type="date">sant Johans tag czü
                                    <expan>sübend<ex>e</ex>n</expan> nu schirst</q>24.06.1411</note></app> czü
                                <expan>eine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>frewntlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> tag <expan>kume<ex>n</ex></expan> wil
                        gen Onelspach, wenn ir ir den tag in <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> czeit <expan>v<ex>er</ex>kündet</expan>
                        vier tag vor, ee daz dann <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> tag sein sol,
                                <expan>ungev<ex>er</ex>lich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>i<ex>n</ex></expan> die <expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>i</expan>
<expan>Urba<ex>n</ex>i</expan>.</ab>
</div>
